system calls in xelix
---------------------


currently, use call_systemcall from syscalls.asm to call a system call

calling:
interrupt no. 81
eax: syscall number
other registers: supplementary information for the syscall, see documentation of each individual syscall
return value: given back in eax

Syscalls at int 81:
1: print
	ebx: pointer to C-String which will be printed to screen
	returns: 0
2: printDec
	ebx: uint32 which will be printed in decimal system
	returns: 0
3: printHex
	ebx: uint32 which will be printed in hexadecimal system
	returns: 0
